      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted using meshes of 2.1M, 4.8M, and 9.6M elements. The Grid Convergence Index (GCI) for the normalized hemolysis index at the worst-case operating point was 3.2%, well below the 10% threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirms second-order convergence. Achieved level exceeds requirement."
    },
