      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments were conducted using bovine blood at 37°C with hematocrit 35±2%. Flow rates were controlled by a calibrated gear pump and verified by an ultrasonic flow meter (±2% accuracy). Rotational speed was monitored by optical tachometer (±10 RPM). All boundary conditions are traceable to calibrated measurements."
    },
    {
