      "rationale": "Across all five flow-speed operating points, the CFD-predicted normalized hemolysis index agreed with experimental measurements within 6–11%. The maximum discrepancy of 11% at the 4 L/min, 2500 RPM point remains within the 15% acceptance threshold. Output comparison is satisfactory at Gradation 2."
    },
    {
