      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) computed by CFD is directly converted to the relative hemolysis index RH used in the COU acceptance criterion via a standardized normalization formula. The QoI used in validation is the same quantity compared against the predicate device, ensuring direct relevance."
