    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for hemolysis index across the COU operating envelope, with all validation points satisfying RH < 1. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The overall credibility assessment supports acceptance of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
